# TASK 5: Make Chat Panel Resizable

## CONTEXT
**Current state:** Fixed 180px chat panel.
**Relevant files:** src/renderer/index.html, src/renderer/styles.css, src/renderer/renderer.js

## OBJECTIVE
Allow dragging the top edge of chat panel to resize it.

## IMPLEMENTATION

### Step 1: Add resize handle HTML
Add as first child of #chat-panel:
```html
<div id="chat-resize-handle"></div>
```

### Step 2: Add handle styles
```css
#chat-resize-handle {
  height: 4px;
  background: transparent;
  cursor: ns-resize;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
#chat-resize-handle:hover {
  background: #4a9eff;
}
```

### Step 3: Add resize logic to renderer.js
Add at end of file:
```javascript
// Chat panel resize
const chatPanel = document.getElementById('chat-panel');
const resizeHandle = document.getElementById('chat-resize-handle');
let isResizing = false;
let startY, startHeight;

resizeHandle.addEventListener('mousedown', (e) => {
  isResizing = true;
  startY = e.clientY;
  startHeight = chatPanel.offsetHeight;
  document.body.style.cursor = 'ns-resize';
  document.body.style.userSelect = 'none';
});

document.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {
  if (!isResizing) return;
  const deltaY = startY - e.clientY;
  const newHeight = Math.min(Math.max(100, startHeight + deltaY), window.innerHeight * 0.6);
  chatPanel.style.height = newHeight + 'px';
});

document.addEventListener('mouseup', () => {
  if (isResizing) {
    isResizing = false;
    document.body.style.cursor = '';
    document.body.style.userSelect = '';
  }
});
```

**Files to modify:** src/renderer/index.html, src/renderer/styles.css, src/renderer/renderer.js

